/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
// For running a DMTCP save and restore operation please follow the 
// guidelines given below
// 
// 
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////



A. To perform a save operation using DMTCP run the target dmtcp_save
B. To restore from the stored checkpoint run the target dmtcp_restore
C. To run both store and restore operations run the target  run_dmtcp 
